            <h1 class="header">Recruiters Nominate Their Favorite Phone Interview Questions</h1>
        <h2 class="subheader"></h2>
        <div class="post-details">
          <h2 class="single-page-h3">
              <a href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/ritikapuri' target='_blank'><img class='author-img' src='http://talent.linkedin.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/Screen-Shot-2014-08-14-at-6.44.54-PM.png' width='24' height='24' /></a>              <span class="author">
              <a href="http://talent.linkedin.com/blog/index.php/author/ritika-puri" title="Posts by Ritika Puri" rel="author">Ritika Puri</a>              </span>
              <span class="timestamp">February 2, 2015            </span>
          </h2>
          <div class='social'>
            <ul class="share-btns">
